### Create a pricing rule
POST https://localhost:7004/api/pricing/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "{{hotelId}}",
  "roomTypeId": "{{roomTypeId}}",
  "ruleType": "Seasonal",
  "name": "Peak Season Pricing",
  "description": "Higher prices during peak tourist season",
  "startDate": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-08-31T23:59:59Z",
  "basePriceModifier": 1.25,
  "fixedPriceAdjustment": 0,
  "minimumPrice": 150.00,
  "maximumPrice": 0,
  "priority": 1
}

### Create a demand-based pricing rule
POST https://localhost:7004/api/pricing/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "{{hotelId}}",
  "roomTypeId": "{{roomTypeId}}",
  "ruleType": "Demand",
  "name": "High Occupancy Pricing",
  "description": "Price increase when hotel occupancy is high",
  "basePriceModifier": 1.15,
  "fixedPriceAdjustment": 0,
  "occupancyThreshold": 0.8,
  "priority": 2
}

### Create a special event pricing rule
POST https://localhost:7004/api/pricing/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "{{hotelId}}",
  "roomTypeId": "{{roomTypeId}}",
  "ruleType": "Special",
  "name": "Christmas Pricing",
  "description": "Special pricing for Christmas period",
  "startDate": "2024-12-20T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-12-26T23:59:59Z",
  "basePriceModifier": 1.5,
  "fixedPriceAdjustment": 50.00,
  "specialEvent": "Christmas",
  "priority": 3
}

### Calculate price
POST https://localhost:7004/api/pricing/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotelId": "{{hotelId}}",
  "roomTypeId": "{{roomTypeId}}",
  "checkInDate": "2024-06-15T14:00:00Z",
  "checkOutDate": "2024-06-18T11:00:00Z",
  "numberOfGuests": 2,
  "numberOfRooms": 1,
  "specialEvent": "Summer",
  "weatherCondition": "Sunny",
  "currentOccupancyRate": 0.85
}

### Get a specific pricing rule
GET https://localhost:7004/api/pricing/rules/{{pricingRuleId}}

### Get hotel pricing for a specific date
GET https://localhost:7004/api/pricing/hotels/{{hotelId}}/pricing?date=2024-06-15

